k.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538627-20200719.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:17:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">香港獨立,唯一出路</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sePGhGL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsePGhGL.jpg&h=1595e083&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95dab2554495dce0d9f4326ae8d415dad80b138c","tid":2114653,"uid":173207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"220c92447dbfd7e2c9c5d9f0898710c4bdd2ded8","tid":2114653,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"身兼資深大律師的行政會議成員湯家驊表示，預計立法會選舉有不少人會被取消參選資格，因為有更多人測試國家安全的底線，若視之為政治本錢，「上得山多終遇虎」，可以被取消資格的機會自然更高，又指《港區國安法》只有一條條文列明，被定罪的人士不能參選，目前引用《港區國安法》取消參選資格的可能性等於零。<br />\n<br />\n被問到《港區國安法》第一章列明，參選時應簽署文件確認擁護《基本法》及香港特區，若不簽署確認書會否違反《港區國安法》，湯家驊在一個電台節目後表示，有關條文是一個原則性指示，並無訂明有法律後果，認為選舉主任仍然是根據選舉相關法例及《基本法》確認提名。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊出席電台節目時表示，政府取消選舉參選人資格是運用現有的選舉法例，《港區國安法》相關的條文是涉及定罪後的情況。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538627-20200719.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538627-20200719.htm&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB5hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=1ae9bfbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538627-20200719.htm&h=a87afa2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538627-20200719.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T06:18:33.000Z","msg":"閃卡藏西環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0829e9c8f7aa85d48a38941db5ee49cbb424824","tid":2114653,"uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2572c2662dd39c98d838cc3fabb1c9cc8d67485","tid":2114653,"uid":268516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea88b07a091793ad6ea615371c35e68eff13701e","tid":2114653,"uid":103156,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:09:1